From edd at debian.org  Thu Sep 13 22:55:58 2018
From: edd at debian.org (Dirk Eddelbuettel)
Date: Thu, 13 Sep 2018 15:55:58 -0500
Subject: [Rcpp-devel] questions Rcpp
